### 测试说明
# 本地启动了一个 Streamable HTTP MCP 服务: http://0.0.0.0:8000/mcp
# 通过 SSE 接口透明代理使用该服务

### 1. 检查服务状态 - 使用 Stream 协议连接远程 Streamable 服务
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/check_status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mcpId": "test-streamable-service",
  "mcpJsonConfig": "{\"mcpServers\": {\"test-service\": {\"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:8000/mcp\"}}}",
  "mcpType": "Persistent",
  "mcpProtocol": "Stream"
}

### 2. 获取 SSE 连接
# 注意: mcpId 需要与上面 check_status 中的 mcpId 保持一致
GET http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service/sse
Accept: text/event-stream

### 3. 发送消息到 MCP 服务
# 在新标签页或终端中运行，模拟客户端发送消息
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "msg-1",
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "test-client",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### 4. 列出可用工具
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "msg-2",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### 5. 调用工具 (根据实际可用的工具调整)
POST http://localhost:8085/mcp/sse/proxy/test-streamable-service/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "msg-3",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "your-tool-name",
    "arguments": {}
  }
}

### 6. 清理服务
DELETE http://localhost:8085/mcp/config/delete/test-streamable-service
Content-Type: application/json

{}
